Appendix A

Social Cost Survey

11/19/2019

Introduction

For the analysis on social cost we needed to quantify exactly how an involuntary and voluntary organ donation system would affect society. The philosophy here is that we can quantify and monetize the cost to society of having prisoner kidneys harvested by simpling asking what compensation they would require, if any, if they were in the poisition of a prisoner. Since we are not giving prisoners standing, these numbers may or may not make it into the final analysis.
